hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Do you need a work permit? bellalift onde comprar no brasil But hold on. Aren’t we meant to be casting off the apron strings and thinking: glass ceiling, rather than glass jars? Actually, I think the two are possibly linked. Any busy businesswoman or executive finds herself, at times (as I do) ‘living in her head’. Your brain’s racing. A million ideas a minute may be jumping around in it. But when the diary itself is jam-packed, there’s something about making actual jam itself that is deeply ‘grounding’ and restorative.
